 Ultra Magnus heard the noise outside. He ran out and saw the battle. His 
spark felt like it was on fire. He saw Hydras and trembled. He screamed no! 
as the foreign mind told him his plans. He had no choice. The blackheart that 
had a grip on the other half of his spark would not be put aside. He seemed 
to nod to the silent power and understand. He pulled out his gun and flew at 
the preds firing.

--part1_93.25938121.2af5347c_boundary
